name: Side By Side Organic Farm
address: HHFM+PWV, Padang Kerta, Karangasem, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: Ketut and his family were very kind and helpful. The food was absolutely amazing and almost all the ingredients are grown on the farm!
review 2:
A very interesting way to visit the forest of Bali. It is a very large and natural farm and the lunch is very fresh and delicious. Katut is very knowledgeable and friendly. Call to book it do not try to go on your own as it will be very difficult.
Prepare to be in heat and a lot of bugs for a good amount of time.
review 3: Loved this place. Perfect break away from the he busy city life and typical vacation. So serene , this is the real detox !
review 4: Difficult to find, no signs. Drove there and searched, in the end - nobody was there. Just a barking dog. We waited for 5 minutes and left.
review 5: Great organic food and beautiful nature.
